<view class="page">
  <view class="section">
    <view class="title">饮食记录</view>
    <view class="subtitle">后续在这里录入食物、餐次、数量和预估摄入热量。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card">
    <view class="subtitle">当前日期</view>
    <view class="title">{{date}}</view>
    <view class="metric-row">
      <view class="metric">
        <text class="metric-value">0</text>
        <text class="metric-label">摄入千卡</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="primary-button">添加食物</button>
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="goWorkout">查看训练</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
